<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٠ - <span class="c2">(١١٨٤)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5898">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى - يَعْنِي ابْنَ سَعِيدٍ </a>-، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدِ اللهِ </a>، أَخْبَرَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٌ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5"><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">« تَلَقَّفْتُ التَّلْبِيَةَ مِنْ فِي رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>»</span>، فَذَكَرَ بِمِثْلِ حَدِيثِهِمْ .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>